  "prompt": "How do I contact Handy customer service?",
  "response": "To contact Handy customer service, you have several options: \n\n1. **Help Center**: Visit Handy's online help center at [help.handy.com](https://help.handy.com). You can find answers to frequently asked questions and solutions to common issues.\n\n2. **Email**: You can email Handy customer support directly at support@handy.com. Make sure to provide detailed information about your issue to get a quicker response.\n\n3. **Phone Support**: If you prefer speaking to a representative, you can call Handy customer service at (888) 844-8880. Phone support is generally available during business hours.\n\n4. **App**: If you use the Handy app, you can navigate to the support or help section within the app to find contact options. You may be able to chat with support representatives directly through the app.\n\n5. **Social Media**: Reach out via Handy's social media platforms like Twitter or Facebook. Sometimes, companies respond quickly to inquiries made through social channels.\n\nBefore contacting Handy, ensure you have all necessary information, such as your account details and the specifics of your issue, to facilitate timely and effective assistance.",
